# AMR-GigaWord 200k

# ::id 0 ::amr-annotator ISI-AMR-01 ::preferred
# ::tok haiti 's ousted president condemned the incarceration of a roman catholic priest and prominent political leader , saying his detention shows conditions for fair elections do not exist .
# ::alignments
(a / and
      :op1 (c / condemn-01
            :ARG0 (p / person
                  :ARG0-of (h / have-org-role-91
                        :ARG1 (g / government-organization
                              :name (n / name
                                    :op1 "Haiti"))
                        :ARG2 (p2 / president))
                  :ARG1-of (o / oust-01))
            :ARG1 (ii / incarcerate-01
                  :ARG1 (a2 / and
                        :op1 (p3 / priest
                              :mod (r / religious-group
                                    :name (n2 / name
                                          :op1 "Catholic")))
                        :op2 (p4 / person
                              :ARG0-of (l / lead-02
                                    :ARG1 (p5 / politics))
                              :mod (p6 / prominent)))))
      :op2 (s / say-01
            :ARG0 p
            :ARG1 (s2 / show-01
                  :ARG0 (d / detain-01
                        :ARG1 a2)
                  :ARG1 (e / exist-01
                        :polarity -
                        :ARG1 (c2 / condition
                              :purpose (e2 / elect-01
                                    :ARG1-of (f / fair-01)))))))

# ::id 1 ::amr-annotator ISI-AMR-01 ::preferred
# ::tok mel c , who had opposed a reunion of the spice girls , has changed her mind .
# ::alignments
(c / change-01
      :ARG0 (p / person
            :name (n / name
                  :op1 "mel"
                  :op2 "c")
            :ARG0-of (o / oppose-01
                  :ARG1 (r / reunite-01
                        :ARG1 (g / girl
                              :ARG0-of (s / spice-01)))))
      :ARG1 (m / mind-05
            :ARG0 p))
